        "solution_html": "<p><span class=\"english\">যুক্তবর্ণ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">দুই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রকার</span><span class=\"english\">। </span><span class=\"english\">যথা</span><span class=\"english\">-১. </span><span class=\"english\">স্বচ্ছ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যুক্তবর্ণ</span><span class=\"english\"> ২. </span><span class=\"english\">অস্বচ্ছ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যুক্তবর্ণ</span><span class=\"english\">। </span><span class=\"english\">প্রশ্নোক্ত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যুক্তবর্ণগুলোর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বিশ্লেষণ</span><span class=\"english\"> ও </span><span class=\"english\">শব্দগঠন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নিম্নরূপ</span><span class=\"english\">:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">ঞ্ছ- ঞ্‌ + ছ = লাঞ্ছনা, বাঞ্ছনীয়</span><span class=\"english\">।</span><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">হ্ন- হ্‌ + ন = চিহ্ন, মধ্যাহ্ন</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বণ্টন</span><span class=\"english\">:</span></p><p><span class=\"english\"></span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যুক্তবর্ণ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">দুই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রকার</span><span class=\"english\"> / </span><span class=\"english\">১. </span><span class=\"english\">স্বচ্ছ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যুক্তবর্ণ</span><span class=\"english\"> ২. </span><span class=\"english\">অস্বচ্ছ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যুক্তবর্ণ</span><span class=\"english\">। </span><span class=\"english\">এটা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">লেখার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span class=\"english\"> ০১ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\"></span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">প্রতিটি যুক্তবর্ণ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বিশ্লেষণ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করার</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span class=\"english\"> ০১ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">পাবে</span><span class=\"english\">। (০১+০১</span><span class=\"english\">=০২</span><span class=\"english\">)</span></p><p><span class=\"english\"></span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যুক্তবর্ণ দিয়ে প্রতিটি শব্দ গ</span><span class=\"english\">ঠনের</span><span class=\"english\"> ০.৫ </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">পাবে</span><span class=\"english\">। (০.৫</span><span class=\"english\">×</span><span class=\"english\">৪=০২</span><span class=\"english\">)</span></p><p><span> </span></p><p><span class=\"english\">নোট</span><span class=\"english\">: </span><span class=\"english\">হসন্তসহ</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">যেকোনো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ধরনের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ভুলের</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">জন্য</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">বরাদ্দকৃত</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">নম্বর</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">কর্তন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করা</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">হবে</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p><span class=\"english\">পরীক্ষক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ভুলগুলো</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">আন্ডারলাইন</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">অবশ্যই</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">ঠিক</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">করে</span><span> </span><span class=\"english\">দিবেন</span><span class=\"english\">।</span></p><p></p>"
